ga
Class GeneticAlgorithmFactory

java.lang.Object
  ga.GeneticAlgorithmFactory

public abstract class GeneticAlgorithmFactory
extends java.lang.Object

An abstract factory class for obtaining information about what GA operators are available on the system. A hash or list of class instances is returned for each operator type.

Author:
Matt Oates
